==English==

{{rank|man's|write|caught|652|below|window|instead|giving}}

===Etymology===
From {{ME.}} ''[[bilooghe]]'' < {{ME.}} ''[[bi]]'' "by" + ''[[looghe]]'' "low".

===Preposition===
'''below'''

#[[lower]] in [[spatial]] [[position]] than
#:''The treasure is buried 2 meters '''below''' the ground.''
#[[lower]] in [[value]] than
#:''The temperature is '''below''' zero.''
#[[downstream]] of
#[[south]] of
#unsuitable to the rank or dignity of
#:''Such petty behavior is '''below''' me.''

====Synonyms====
*(''lower in spatial position than''): [[beneath]], [[under]], [[underneath]]
*(''lower in value than''): [[under]]
*(''downstream of''): [[downstream]]
*(''unsuitable to the rank or dignity of''): [[beneath]]

====Antonyms====
*(''lower in spatial position than''): [[above]], [[over]]
*(''lower in value than''): [[over]]
*(''downstream of''): [[upstream]]


